title: Brother MFC-J480DW - Loading the ink
description:
Learn how to install or replace the ink in your Brother MFC-J460DW, MFC-J480DW, or MFC-J485DW inkjet all-in-one printer.

The model shown is the MFC-J480DW

Models covered:
Brother MFC-J460DW inkjet all-in-one
Brother MFC-J480DW inkjet all-in-one
Brother MFC-J485DW inkjet all-in-one

For more videos, tutorials, and FAQs visit our support site at: http://www.brother-usa.com/support
